edit: oh jeez i just noticed the title, not sure why 'nice' is in there. sorry about that gang</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/s3YEIr9</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CeleryMan7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Who's up for a preposterously long thread about why you don't know jack about Russia? Everyone? Neat.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/7yLDBCL</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/91eoCSu.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Sorry I said you don't know jack. I'm sure you know some things. I knew some of these things, but the picture they paint put together is dire for Russia, and it pretty much killed any hope I had of someone staging a military coup to get them out of the mess Putin has made for them. 

To find out why read on, and fair warning, it's *really* long. Maybe just favourite and forget right now. No-one will judge.

(Oh, and pretty sure English isn't Kamil's first language so cut him some slack, word around the campfire is your Russian isn't so hot either, pal.)</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CCJyUQv.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>How's it going? So proud of you for making it this far. You're half way!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/VtdRaSp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Ok so I lied a bit before, you were halfway through *this* post. I've actually run out of juice because the screenshot app I use can't go any further than this. To be fair this screenshot was almost 25000 pixels tall (split in half for imgur). 

If you've come this far and still want to read the rest there's about 30 more tweets starting here. https://twitter.com/kamilkazani/status/1502733326330773508</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/7yLDBCL</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TheGhostofElizabethShue]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fuck Budget</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/btHlf4r</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9I1Y7jj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Finally moving out of trash apartment complex to a new state. Plan was to take some of our stuff with us and put it in storage near where we’re moving, do some interviews and apply for apartments. When we came out last night to start the drive, the full truck was gone.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Ecq6xuw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We drive to the tow yard that’s posted at our complex they don’t have it. Call the non emergency police, they track it down to Budget towing it cuz the complex told them to. After hours of getting the ring around we find where it was dropped off only for the people there to say it’s not there anymore. At this point I’ve had to reschedule an important job interview, on the verge of a panic attack, and I don’t think my partner has ever been this angry.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/koj5uUu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>We go there in person and it is there! The mechanic had moved it without telling them and they couldn’t see it from their office. After getting the whole story, they say we can go and don’t have to pay any towing fees! Only to find out that the truck won’t start because said mechanic “took something out so they can’t just drive away without paying tow fees”. Except 1) no one told him to do this 2) we don’t have to pay, we have permission from 3 people above him and 3) mechanic won’t be in until Monday.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/t7OFKpL.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>They finally get ahold of the mechanic and verbally tear him to shreds and make him walk through another employee how to fix the truck. Ten minutes later we drive off with no towing fees and an extra two days to our rental at no cost to us!

 **Most Viral Edit: I’d like to thank the academy and viewers just like you**</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/btHlf4r</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Technicolorluver]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Sky Diving Moves</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/NWDT4s8</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9ipFcRt.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/NWDT4s8</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[liangjianyi7]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>lol</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/kbLq5RC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/D2kKGLm.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.rawstory.com/peoples-convoy-dc-truckers/</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/kbLq5RC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[maximilianfragglebottom]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Since i saw some coub posts, here are some fun ones</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MLzcKdj</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7pdVMEK.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tDfhVXr.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zr4m3y6.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Za3jJGb.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/NmYTDkD.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v7TUVzX.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/hYvf4oa.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.